<% page_title "Whitehall admin style guide" %>

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Whitehall admin style guide</h1>
</div>

<p class="lead">Whitehall admin UI is powered by <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/2.3.2/">bootstrap 2.3.2</a> (using the <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap-sass/tree/v2.3.2.2">bootstrap-sass gem</a>) with some help from the <a href="https://github.com/alphagov/govuk_frontend_toolkit">govuk_frontend_toolkit</a>. This guide partially documents how we use bootstrap, where whitehall styles have diverged from default styles and any custom styles needed to fill in the gaps.</p>

<h2>Grid</h2>
<p class="lead">Whitehall uses the <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/2.3.2/scaffolding.html#fluidGridSystem">bootstrap 2.3.2 fluid grid</a>.</p>

